{"tid":2379777,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"觀塘示威案被告指控警暴 疑電油淋下體兼插贓嫁禍","createTime":"2021-01-25T12:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T13:47:47.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de94f2d060a6ee247af1a32ac9923a58c23d9afb","tid":2379777,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"兩少年被控前年10月破壞觀塘港鐵站升降機和管有武器等罪，案件今日續審。繼案發時15歲的被告早前投訴遭警方動武逼供，同案19歲被告學生今作供時亦指稱遭受警暴，包括被捕時遭警員壓<span class=\"red\">臉磨警車鐵網、用疑似電油淋下體、插贓嫁禍、揮拳打顎及放物件於手指上壓指模</span>。<br />\n<br />\n警員再説：「哦！咁X多野嘅！」被告回應：「X！你塞畀我嘅！」此時車上有人説：「X！傻仔嚟嘅，架車有cam㗎。」高指事後感到「個袋重咗」。<br />\n<br />\n到了警署下車時，高指大批警員兩邊排成人牆，不斷向他恥笑及講粗口，一名便衣男子走近向他説「X你老母死曱甴」，同時向他下顎揮拳。他又指於警署被反鎖期間，有人將他的手指按壓於物件上。"},{"pid":"11b15144098cf34b35afb5178a80d74a3e5a745b","tid":2379777,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/I4WHBJT7GFAZTF5BJF43YNUM6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FI4WHBJT7GFAZTF5BJF43YNUM6U%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABd4mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=99a54ce9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FI4WHBJT7GFAZTF5BJF43YNUM6U%2F&h=0e3e0602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/I4WHBJT7GFAZTF5BJF43YNUM6U/</a>"},{"pid":"964e9d6f32e3d1c1b28fcd163ff320d9f596dc1d","tid":2379777,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f7e398e34cd2dd89d7c95fb0bd04773ff6e176","tid":2379777,"uid":80393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f